                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="info-card">
                                <h4>@LanguageService.GetLocalizedText("NasÄ±l HesaplanÄ±r?", "How to Calculate?")</h4>
                                <p>@LanguageService.GetLocalizedText("1. En Ã— Boy Ã— YÃ¼kseklik hesaplayÄ±n (cm)\n2. Sonucu 6000'e bÃ¶lÃ¼n (IATA standardÄ±)\n3. Adet ile Ã§arpÄ±n\n4. GerÃ§ek aÄŸÄ±rlÄ±k ile karÅŸÄ±laÅŸtÄ±rÄ±n\n5. BÃ¼yÃ¼k olanÄ± Ã¼crete konu aÄŸÄ±rlÄ±k olarak alÄ±n", "1. Calculate Width Ã— Length Ã— Height (cm)\n2. Divide result by 6000 (IATA standard)\n3. Multiply by quantity\n4. Compare with actual weight\n5. Take the greater as chargeable weight")</p>
